The paper focuses on the service integration of online social networks, which falls under the category of social networks (cs.SOC) and social media (cs.MM). The analysis of the social graph and the machine learning model for predicting high PageRank users involve information retrieval (cs.IR) and cyber security (cs.CYBER) techniques. Overall, the paper's main focus on service integration and social networks suggests that cs.SI is the most likely sub-category.
